title: Easy Access to 1-45, Convenient Laundry Facilities, Wet/Dry Bars
posting_body: ['Welcome to Forest Creek Apartments in Conroe, Texas, where we consider our residents family.', 'Our comfortable community at Forest Creek Apartment Homes offers beautiful one and two-bedroom apartment homes equipped with walk in closets, outside storage, and fireplaces.', 'Our friendly community is conveniently located in Conroe, Texas near downtown, The Woodlands Mall, and Lake Conroe, only 30 minutes from Sam Houston State University.', 'Enjoy maintenance free living with exceptional amenities including private balconies or patios, a 24/7 Fitness Room, and two sparkling pools.', 'With everything so close, life seems to become that much easier.', 'Forest Creek has something for everyone, and we hope to see you soon!', 'Call now to schedule your tour!', '-Spacious 1 & 2 Bedrooms', '-Cozy Wood Burning Fireplaces', '-Beautifully Landscaped Community', '-Business Center', '-30 minutes from Sam Houston State University', '-Variety of Large Floor Plans', '-Professional Management', '-Cable/Satellite Ready', '-Decorative Mini-Blinds & Vertical Blinds', '-Fully Equipped Kitchens', '-Easy Access to 1-45', '-Ample Cabinet Space & Large Walk', 'In -Closets', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.']
